data.description: Motivated Seller! Seller says make an offer. All new stainless appliances. Outstanding view of the mountains from the back porches. Immaculate and pristine condition. Kitchen with island and food prep sink. Large formal dining room currently used as an office. Covered breezeway between garage and house. Finished bonus room over garage will be sold with pool table and treadmill. Plenty of room for horses or a pool. Red barn with plenty of storage space. Beautiful wrap around porches for entertaining and loads of space for outdoor fun.
